==Slovak==
===Personal pronoun===
'''[[si#Slovak|si]]''' ''or'' '''sebe'''

Replaces the the [[dative]] of a personal pronoun when the [[subject]] is of the same [[person]] as the dative [[object]]. Roughly comparable with ''to oneself'' or ''for oneself''.
:'''Kupujem ''si'' topánky.'''&ndash;''I am buying "me" shoes.''
:'''Komu kupuješ topánky? Sebe.'''&ndash;''Who are you buying the shoes for? Myself.''

